# Non-secret runtime paths loaded by `moeka.sh`.
#
# Copy to `.env` and edit to suit. Use absolute paths — `~` is NOT expanded
# inside .env files.
#
# Both files (.env and keys.env) live at the repo root and are gitignored.

# --- Moeka instance directory -----------------------------------------------
# One tree holding everything: config.json, agent identity docs (SOUL/AGENTS/
# HEARTBEAT/TOOLS/USER.md), skills, memory, sessions, media, cron, history.
#
# Default is `~/.nanobot` to stay compatible with upstream nanobot paths.
# `git init` it to carry a full agent identity between machines.
MOEKA_WORKSPACE=/home/youruser/.nanobot
